('de1bc355-3804-5c67-b7ae-14f3a7866e50', '42240ac0-169c-42fd-b66f-b493530af6bc', 'The students like to ___ to the music in the classroom.', '學生們喜歡在教室裡隨著音樂跳舞。', 'dance', 'sing', 'sleep', 'study', 'dance 為動詞，意為「跳舞」。', '看到音樂節奏強烈時，就想去 dance。', '2026-07-07 02:40:17', '2026-07-07 02:40:17'),
